葉里溫汗國的疆域過去屬於[[薩法維王朝|薩法維王朝]]的{{le|葉里溫省 (薩法維王朝)|Erivan Province (Safavid Empire)|葉里溫省}}，[[阿夫沙爾王朝|阿夫沙爾王朝]]建立後，[[納迪爾沙|納迪爾沙]]將此地區分為葉里溫汗國、[[納希切萬汗國|納希切萬汗國]]、[[卡拉巴赫汗國|卡拉巴赫汗國]]與{{le|占賈汗國|Ganja Khanate}}{{sfn|Bournoutian|2006|pages=214–215}}，葉里溫汗國與納希切萬汗國的疆土屬於{{le|波斯亞美尼亞|Iranian Armenia (1502–1828)}}{{sfn|Bournoutian|1980|pages=1–2}}。納迪爾沙死後伊朗陷入混亂，葉里溫汗國先後成為[[桑德王朝|桑德王朝]]與[[卡扎爾王朝|卡扎爾王朝]]的附庸{{sfn|Bournoutian|2006|page=215}}，其中後者會派任卡扎爾王室成員作為葉里溫汗國的統治者<ref name="Bournoutian 2002 p. 215">{{harvnb|Bournoutian|2002|page=215}}. "'''Iranians''', in order to save the rest of eastern Armenia, heavily subsidized the region '''and appointed a capable governor, Hosein Qoli Khan, to administer it'''."</ref>{{sfn|Bournoutian|2004|pages=519–520}}。葉里溫汗國分為15個{{tsl|en|Mahallah||區}}，以[[波斯語|波斯語]]為官方語言<ref>{{cite book|last1=Swietochowski|first1=Tadeusz|authorlink = Tadeusz Swietochowski|title=Russian Azerbaijan, 1905-1920: The Shaping of a National Identity in a Muslim Community|date=2004|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=Cambridge|isbn=978-0521522458|page=12|quote=(...) and Persian continued to be the official language of the judiciary and the local administration [even after the abolishment of the khanates].}}<!--|accessdate=3 December 2015--></ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Pavlovich|first1=Petrushevsky Ilya|title=Essays on the history of feudal relations in Armenia and Azerbaijan in XVI - the beginning of XIX centuries|date=1949|publisher=LSU them. Zhdanov|page=7|quote=(...) The language of official acts not only in Iran proper and its fully dependant Khanates, but also in those Caucasian khanates that were semi-independent until the time of their accession to the Russian Empire, and even for some time after, '''was New Persian (Farsi).''' It played the role of the literary language of class feudal lords as well.}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|first=Homa|last=Katouzian|title= Iranian history and politics|url=https://archive.org/details/iranianhistorypo00kato|publisher=Routledge|date=2003|page=[https://archive.org/details/iranianhistorypo00kato/page/128 128]|isbn=978-0415297547|quote=Indeed, since the formation of the Ghaznavids state in the tenth century until the fall of Qajars at the beginning of the twentieth century, most parts of the Iranian cultural regions were ruled by Turkic-speaking dynasties most of the time. At the same time, the official language was Persian, the court literature was in Persian, and most of the chancellors, ministers, and mandarins were Persian speakers of the highest learning and ability.}}</ref>，地方官僚為仿照[[德黑蘭|德黑蘭]]中央政府的官僚系統設立<ref name="Bournoutian 1982 p. 86">{{harvnb|Bournoutian|1982|page=86}}. "The Khan Hosein Qoli Khan's '''efficient administration''' soon transformed the region. He '''modeled his bureaucracy on that of the <u>central government</u>''', dividing power between tribal and settled groups (...) In essence '''the Erevan administration, like its counterpart in Tehran''', was organized into three branches (...)"</ref>。

十九世紀初，俄羅斯帝國併吞了[[卡特利-卡赫季王國|卡特利-卡赫季王國]]，1804年發動[[俄罗斯－波斯战争_(1804年－1813年)|俄罗斯－波斯战争]]，葉里溫成為波斯抵禦俄羅斯的防衛中心{{sfn|Kettenhofen|Bournoutian|Hewsen|1998|pages=542–551}}。1804年，俄軍在{{le|帕維爾·齊賈諾夫|Pavel Tsitsianov}}率領下攻擊葉里溫，{{le|Siege of Erivan (1804)|葉里溫之圍|包圍葉里溫城}}，後來被卡札爾王朝的儲君[[阿巴斯·米爾札|阿巴斯·米爾札]]率軍擊退{{sfn|Kettenhofen|Bournoutian|Hewsen|1998|pages=542–551}}。1807年，卡札爾王朝沙阿[[法特赫-阿里沙·卡扎爾|法特赫-阿里沙·卡扎爾]]任命{{le|侯賽因·汗·薩達爾|Hossein Khan Sardar}}為葉里溫汗國統治者（[[汗_(頭銜)|汗]]）與[[阿拉斯河|阿拉斯河]]以北波斯軍隊的指揮官（{{le|薩達爾|Sardar}}）<ref name="Bournoutian 2002 p. 215"/><ref>{{harvnb|Bournoutian|2004|pages=519–520}}. "ḤOSAYNQOLI KHAN SARDĀR-E IRAVĀNI; important '''governor in the early Qajar period''' (b. ca. 1742, d. 1831). (...) Requiring a strong and loyal governor to command the fortress of Erevan against the Russian advances during the first Russo-Persian War (1804-13), '''the shah appointed Ḥosaynqoli as the commander-in-chief (sardār) of the Persian forces''' north of the Araxes (Aras) River."</ref>，侯賽因·汗·薩達爾統治下的葉里溫汗國相當繁榮，為卡札爾王朝的模範省{{sfn|Kettenhofen|Bournoutian|Hewsen|1998|pages=542–551}}，他設立有效率的管理體制讓當地的亞美尼亞人恢復了對波斯統治的信心{{sfn|Kettenhofen|Bournoutian|Hewsen|1998|pages=542–551}}<ref name="Bournoutian 1982 p. 86"/>。

1808年，俄軍將領[[伊萬·古多維奇|伊萬·古多維奇]]率軍襲擊葉里溫，亦被擊退，1813年《[[古利斯坦條約|古利斯坦條約]]》簽訂後，波斯失去了大部分高加索的領土，葉里溫與[[大不里士|大不里士]]成為兩國攻防的前線{{sfn|Kettenhofen|Bournoutian|Hewsen|1998|pages=542–551}}。1826年，[[俄罗斯－波斯战争_(1826年－1828年)|最後一次俄罗斯－波斯战争]]爆發<ref>{{cite book|editor1-last=Dowling|editor1-first=Timothy C.|title=Russia at War: From the Mongol Conquest to Afghanistan, Chechnya, and Beyond|date=2015|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=978-1598849486|page=729|quote=In May 1826, Russia therefore occupied Mirak, in the Erivan khanate, in violation of the Treaty of Gulistan.}}</ref>，戰爭初期波斯成功奪回許多於1813年失去的領土，但隔年俄羅斯在[[阿巴薩巴德堡|-{阿巴薩巴德堡}-]]（位於納希切萬汗國）、{{le|薩達爾堡|Sardar's Fortress}}（位於葉里溫汗國）與葉里溫大敗波斯軍隊，於1827年10月2日攻陷葉里溫。1828年2月，波斯被迫簽訂《[[土庫曼恰伊條約|土庫曼恰伊條約]]》，將葉里溫汗國與其他[[阿拉斯河|阿拉斯河]]以北的領土割讓給[[俄羅斯帝國|俄羅斯帝國]]{{sfn|Kettenhofen|Bournoutian|Hewsen|1998|pages=542–551}}。

